              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Activity of uranium foils after irradiation",
                "was measured by X-ray HPGe -spectrometer (50 mm2",
                "sensitive area, FWHM=150 for 55Fe) which detects 75",
                "keV gamma-rays from decay of 239U with half-life of",
                "23.5 min. In order to measure activity of activated",
                "Au-foils the HPGe-70 cc detector was used with",
                "FWHM=2.5 keV at 1332 keV gamma transmission of 60Co."
              ]
            }
          ],
